text: Thank you The Big Call for bringing me to these great products. I have more energy than I have had in years in just 5 weeks, I really can't wait to see how I feel after 5 months. The staff at Boomers is very knowledgeable and helpful, the funny thing is, they all seem to have the same sound and mannerism's at bob. It's like they're clones, it's cool. God is so good.
